  "title": "Retail Sales Associate (Photo studio) [Boon Keng | 5 days | up to $3,000 + Commission] - LCYL",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Retail Sales Associate (Photo studio)</strong></h3><p><strong>5 days, 10am-8pm (off day on Monday + 1 weekend)</strong></p><p><strong>Basic salary $2400- $3000 + Commission</strong></p><p><strong>Location: Serangoon Rd, Singapore 328244 (Potong Pasir)</strong></p><p><u><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Promoting photo packages to graduates who will be here for their graduation gown collection.</li><li>Provide professional advice to customers with regards to their photos</li><li>Help to prepare customers for their photo shoot.</li><li>Provide administrative support.</li><li><strong>Assist graduates in their gown fitting.</strong></li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>With any retail sales experience </li><li>Immediate starter or short notice is highly preferred</li></ul><p><u><strong>Benefits:</strong></u></p><ul><li>2 meals provided per day</li><li>Off day on weekend</li><li>Closed on PH</li></ul><p><br />Cheong Yeat Long | R25145358</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</p>",
